snippet.title: SM64 StarRevenge 2: Night of Doom - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Why would you even play this hack? Like there is no fun in playing this endless dump of quicksand and lava, just go play any other hack I made and don't waste your time getting the 152 stars of this.

But if you are braindead enough, then here you go:
